      "content": "you mentioned the \"reality\" is that benefits favor capital owners. but isn't that just one perspective? surely the data on whether supply-side policies actually work is still pretty inconclusive and subject to different economic modeling. why does it seem like you're treating the redistribution effect as the definitive outcome?",
